1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:02,713
Real work rarely stays in one mode.

2
00:00:02,663 --> 00:00:12,538
A project may begin with exploration, use asking to remove one uncertainty, move into collaboration to shape the artifact, and finish with delegation for repeatable execution.

3
00:00:12,538 --> 00:00:16,817
Start with the least autonomous mode that can produce the next useful result.

4
00:00:16,817 --> 00:00:19,134
This is not fear of automation.

5
00:00:19,134 --> 00:00:23,144
It is a way to learn the task boundary before expanding execution.

6
00:00:23,144 --> 00:00:25,355
Evidence earns more autonomy.

7
00:00:25,355 --> 00:00:27,480
Use four switch signals.

8
00:00:27,480 --> 00:00:35,807
Switch when the desired output becomes clearer, when a judgment call appears, when evidence contradicts the plan, or when the consequence of error changes.

9
00:00:35,807 --> 00:00:39,079
Each signal changes the proper human-agent balance.

10
00:00:39,079 --> 00:00:41,586
Imagine preparing a customer launch.

11
00:00:41,586 --> 00:00:43,961
Explore the audience and risks.

12
00:00:43,961 --> 00:00:46,307
Ask for one missing comparison.

13
00:00:46,307 --> 00:00:49,605
Collaborate on the positioning and acceptance criteria.

14
00:00:49,605 --> 00:00:52,884
Delegate the asset checks and scheduled publication.

15
00:00:52,884 --> 00:00:55,884
Then return to human review at the release gate.

16
00:00:55,884 --> 00:01:02,509
Record each handoff in one line: current mode, next result, owner, evidence, and stop condition.

17
00:01:02,509 --> 00:01:08,096
That tiny log prevents silent expansion and makes recovery easier when a task is interrupted.

18
00:01:08,096 --> 00:01:12,288
The loop is simple: choose, run, inspect, and reroute.

19
00:01:12,288 --> 00:01:15,346
Do not reward an agent for staying autonomous.

20
00:01:15,346 --> 00:01:20,048
Reward the workflow for producing a correct, useful, and accountable outcome.

21
00:01:20,048 --> 00:01:23,711
First, Start with the least autonomous mode that can work.

22
00:01:23,711 --> 00:01:27,557
Second, Switch when uncertainty or consequence changes.

23
00:01:27,557 --> 00:01:30,961
Third, Record evidence before expanding autonomy.
